=== Deaths in Suez ===
  +   +
The city of Suez has seen the most violence of the protests thus far. Three of the seven documented deaths have occurred in Suez. Reports from eye witnesses have suggested that the death toll in Suez may be significantly higher, in what has been described as a "massacre". These reports cannot be confirmed as media coverage is banned from Suez.<ref name="rawstory.com"/>
